Motivation: To understand the grammatical structure of the input text, which can help in parsing sentences, identifying subjects, verbs, and objects, and understanding the overall meaning of the text.

Behavior change: The pipeline will now tag each word in the input text with its corresponding part of speech (e.g., noun, verb, adjective, etc.).

